reviewText: This video is Ironman Magazine's Sexy Swimsuit Spectacular.  Features interviews and swimsuit photoshoots of various fitness models such as the statuesque Ahmo Hight, Kawni Gilroy, Midajah, Mimi Wagner, Sherry Goggin, Camille Jones, and Buffy Lawrence.  Some of them may be unfamiliar to you, but remember that this was done in 1996 and a whole new era of fitness models are out there now in Maxim or doing WWF.  All the models are very beautiful and in great shape, note that some of the models will pose topless which is always a good thing. Lighting and video are very clear with some nice closeup work.
